<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id913256e6-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s9547"><num value="9547">§ 9547.</num><heading> Termination</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The provisions of this subchapter shall terminate on the date that is 5 years after <date date="2017-08-02">August 2, 2017</date>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id913256e7-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/pl/115/44/tII/s258">Pub. L. 115–44, title II, § 258</ref>, <date date="2017-08-02">Aug. 2, 2017</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/131/934">131 Stat. 934</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
